de.oaam.model.oaam.mapping

Interface MappingContainerA

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ElementA, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Mapping, Supmapping
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MappingContainerAImpl, MappingImpl, SupmappingImpl

    public interface MappingContainerA
extends ElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Container A'. The root element of the mapping model.

    The following features are supported:

    • Device Assignments
    • Sub Device Assignments
    • Connection Assignments
    • Task Assignments
    • Signal Assignments
    • Supmapping
    See Also:
    MappingPackage.getMappingContainerA()
